kareyyāti? Āmantā. Hañci kappaṭṭho cetiyaṃ abhidakkhiṇaṃ kareyya, no ca vata re vattabbe – ‘‘kappaṭṭho kusalaṃ cittaṃ na paṭilabheyyā’’ti…pe….

